1. **HIGH — Early returns omit the header (functional bug)**: The loading, error, and empty-state guard branches at lines 237–259 return bare centered divs with no header bar. Users who land on Graph view during a slow fetch or API error have no visible List tab to navigate back with. Fix: hoist the shared header out of the guard branches so it renders unconditionally.

