|--------|-------|
| Files analyzed | 2 (`GraphView.tsx`, `GraphView.test.tsx`) |
| Simplifications applied | 3 |
| Net line change | 0 (indent-only + condition rewrites) |
| Validation | PASS (no new lint errors or type errors — pre-existing warnings confirmed pre-existing) |
